title: Genaside II
text:
Genaside II was a British electronic group active in the 1990s and early 2000s. Their music started as rave, developing into jungle, breakbeat and big beat. Its members were Kao Bonez,Chilly Phatz, Charlie Meatz and Killerman Archer.
Their 1991 song "Narra Mine" provided a sample for The Prodigy 1996 track Firestarter. Several years before, another The Prodigy track, Jericho, was remixed by Genaside II.
